//! Well-known primitive constant KIds.
//!
//! Content-addresses are hardcoded blake3 hashes matching the kernel's
//! `build_primitives` in `src/ix/kernel/ingress.rs`. Generated by
//! `lake test -- rust-kernel-build-primitives`.
//!
//! `Primitives<M>` stores `KId<M>` values, resolved from the environment
//! so that names match in both Meta and Anon modes.

